The paper discusses adversarial learning in deep networks for transfer learning, which is a common topic in the machine learning community. The paper specifically focuses on partial transfer learning, which relaxes the shared label space assumption. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). Among these, machine learning and computer vision are the most likely sub-categories as they are directly related to the topic of the paper.
